Arguments

x

a Catalog object
i

which catalog elements to extract
j

Invalid
...

additional arguments (for example secondary a vector of elements to match against like emails(x) or owners(x) by default this is names(x))
value

For updating, an object of the appropriate class and size to insert
drop

Invalid
name

for $, the same as i for [[

Value

A subset of x if extracting, otherwise x duly modified
